This light also has an energy-efficient electronic ballast for instant-on with a no flicker start. Fulfill the photo-biological requirement of desert reptiles with the Zilla T8 Reptile Strip Desert Light Fixture.

fields.name: Frisco Loofah Swing Bird Toy
fields.description: A whole lot of fun is about to swing on into your feathered friend’s life with this loofah swing bird toy, from Frisco by Chewy! The loofah is great for perching, swinging, nibbling and even shredding. Each swing toy is crafted by hand, giving each one its own unique quirks and features, a true one of a kind! It even comes with a clasp and hook so that you can hang it anywhere for playdates.

fields.name: Doggy Do Good Certified Compostable Premium Dog & Cat Waste Bags, Small Handle Bags - On Rolls + Dispenser, 60 count
fields.description: Pick up after your furry friend with these Doggy Do Good Certified Compostable Premium Dog & Cat Waste Bags, Small Handle Bags - On Rolls + Dispenser! These scent-free, tear-free, leak-proof small waste bags are thick (20 microns thick) and tough, keeping the contents and unpleasant odors inside the bag where they belong. They are 38% vegetable based and made from corn starch, an annually renewable source, along with other bio-based proprietary components. Safer for the environment than polyethylene plastic bags, these Doggy Do Good bags break down in your properly managed Home Compost—this helps keep parks and neighborhoods clean and green! Since these waste bags are soft to the touch, they don’t stick to each other, which makes them paws-itively easy to open. And since they are scent-free they won’t bother pet parents who are sensitive to fragrances! These small bags measure 4.5 in. x 11.0 in. (folded) / 8.5 in. x 11.0 in with gusset expanded, making them a paw-fect option for small dogs, toy breeds and puppies. The gusseted side panels expand for maximum capacity! There are 15 bags per roll and the core of each roll is made from recycled materials. These rolls fit in any standard-sized poop bag dispenser. The included heavy-duty dispenser is built to last! It even has a stainless-steel carabiner clip, so you can clip it to your leash or doggie bag—keep it attached during walks, so you are always prepared! And you can feel extra good knowing that Doggy Do Good does good for the environment because they are part of a group of organizations that pledge a minimum of 1% of annual sales to environmental causes. Doggy Do Good donates an additional portion of proceeds to rescues and animal welfare organizations, too!

fields.name: OraVet Plaque Prevention Dog Dental Gel
fields.description: Keep your pet’s mouth fresh and clean the OraVet Plaque Prevention Gel for Pets. A great solution for pets who don’t tolerate brushing well, this gel acts as an invisible barrier to prevent bacteria from sticking to the surface of the teeth—which in turn will help prevent the formation of harmful plaque and tartar. Tasteless and odorless, it’s easily applied by swabbing over the gum lines with the included applicator, making at-home dental care a breeze. Just use once a week in between regular dental cleanings, and take pride in knowing that regular dental care supports your dog’s overall health.

fields.name: PoopShark Leash Pouch & Poopbag Holder Dog Poop Dispenser, Black

fields.description: With the PoopShark Leash Pouch & Poopbag Holder Dog Poop Dispenser, you’re always ready to clean up after your furbaby. The pouch is a paw-some way to carry folded paper bags, repurposed plastic bags and treats on your pup’s leash. The carabiner easily attaches the pouch to your leash at two points, so it won’t swing around as you walk. The drawstring closure is simple and secure, and waterproof recycled polyester keeps those poop bags dry.

fields.name: Zoo Med Turtle Clean Filter 318 Aquatic Turtle Tank Filter
fields.description: Help keep your paddling pal’s pad clean with the Zoo Med 318 Turtle Clean Submersible Reptile Tank Filter. Claw-fect for your turtle habitat, this filter is designed to work on tanks up to 30 gallons. It features a combination of mechanical, chemical and biological filtration methods. This fully-submersible filter for your reptile tank includes dual intake ports to help prevent debris from clogging the unit. It comes complete with a packet of two activated carbon and filter sponges that are easy to change as needed.

fields.name: Go Pet Club 32-in Large Perch Cat Tree Condo
fields.description: Shhh, don’t wake your feline friend as she comfortably snoozes in her Go Pet Club 32-in Cat Tree Condo with Large Perch. This tree features an oversized bottom condo with walls and a roof for ideal privacy when nap time rolls around. The top and center perches provide surfaces for your best bud to sit, lounge and keep an eye on her surroundings while the sisal-wrapped post is made for safe scratching. Crafted in a durable wood and finished with a soft faux-fur, your pal will have no problem settling into this cozy tree. When your girl is feeling playful, she can swat away at the dangly rope toy!

fields.name: Frisco Outdoor Waterproof Stinkproof PVC Rope Leash
fields.description: Looking for the right leash for your water-loving dog? The Frisco Outdoor Waterproof Stink-Proof PVC Rope Leash is perfect for dogs who enjoy a swim and pet parents who want to leave that tell-tale funk behind on the trail! This classic leash is made with polyester rope and coated in matte PVC that resists water and odor-causing bacteria. It features a lobster clasp that helps keep your pup securely leashed, and at the other end there’s a convenient D-ring where you can attach a waste bag dispenser. When you hit the road together, just grab this leash and you’re ready to go. Plus, it's available in three colors so you can perfectly match it to your pup’s style and personality.

fields.name: Weaver Leather Stacy Westfall Stick & String Horse Stick
fields.description: Teach your mane man some new tricks with the Weaver Leather Stacy Westfall Stick and String Horse Stick. This stick and string horse training aid is designed to be durable and lightweight. It features a double core that creates a great feel and improved accuracy. The stick is crafted using fiberglass and is equipped with a golf-club style handle for a comfortable grip. The string is a quarter of an inch wide and six feet long including the popper.

fields.name: Frisco Stretchy Dog & Cat Fleece Vest
fields.description: A fleece vest makes a great addition to anyone’s cold-weather wardrobe, even your pet! These cozy, polyester fleece vests are made of stretchy fabric, and they’re thin enough to work as a layering piece and just warm enough to work as a standalone vest if your dog only needs a light layer to stay comfy during cold weather. Made with a pullover design, so it’s easy to put on and always keeps your pet cozy.

fields.name: PetRageous Designs Fishbone Kitty Ceramic Cat Dish
fields.description: Add a little charm to mealtime with the Fishbone Kitty Cat Dish from PetRageous Designs! This handmade ceramic stoneware saucer can stand to frequent use and cleanings and the design features a lovely cat silhouette against a white and taupe fishbone pattern across the basin. This 2.5-ounce dish the perfect size for serving up a delectable meal for your feline friend in style. Plus, it’s completely dishwasher and microwave safe so heating and cleaning are easy!

fields.name: Gatsby Premium 1200D Heavyweight Waterproof Turnout Horse Blanket
fields.description: **Remember to measure for the perfect fit.** The Gatsby Premium 1200D Heavyweight Waterproof Turnout Horse Blanket is highly durable, perfect for those equines who love to horse around in turnout. It’s both waterproof and breathable for years of use in wet weather conditions. The 1200 denier ripstop outer shell and polyester lining help to keep your horse cozy and dry, while 250 grams of polyfill add warmth. Criss-cross nylon surcingles and adjustable nylon leg straps ensure a secure fit. The quick clip chest straps and double-buckle front closures are super easy to adjust and use.

fields.name: Quick-Tag Personalized Dog & Cat ID Tag, Metallic Gold
fields.description: This gold-planted, brass Quick-Tag Personalized Dog & Cat ID tag can be laser engraved on both sides with three lines of personalized text—add her name, an emergency phone number, her address or even her medical conditions. Now, everyone will know who your furry friend is, so they can safely get her back home in case she ever gets lost! And since it’s laser-engraved and not simply printed on, your pet’s information will stay clear and visible through endless days of play.

fields.name: SunCoast Sugar Gliders Wholesome Balance Sweet Potato Flavored Sugar Glider Food
fields.description: SunCoast Sugar Gliders Wholesome Balance Sweet Potato Flavored Sugar Glider Food is a soy-free and filler-free formula that’s crafted with real chicken because sugar gliders need real animal protein in their diet. This recipe was developed by an animal nutritionist and contains 32% protein. It is highly satiating, meaning your sugar glider buddy may eat less as she feels satisfied sooner. And since it is an essential free feed, this recipe won’t spoil if left out like fresh foods will. This sugar glider formula is a great option for all life stages past weaning, and it’s available in different flavors (sold separately), so you can find the recipe that’s right for your furry friend!
